{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a fully editable Shopify theme section called “Airline savings comparison”.
    
    Design:
    - Two-column layout on desktop
    - Left side: heading, body text, airline/company name cards, CTA button, and trust text underneath
    - Right side: savings badge and two comparison cards
    - Premium clean ecommerce style for a travel bag product page
    - On mobile: stack left content first, comparison second
    - Fully responsive and editable from the Shopify theme editor
    
    Important:
    - The airline/company cards must be editable text fields.
    - Add 6 airline/company card settings by default.
    - If an airline/company text field is empty, hide that card completely.
    - The CTA button must link back to the top/product section of the page.
    - Use a customizable button link field. Default link should be #MainProduct-template--product or #product-form, whichever works best.
    - All texts, colors, spacing, font sizes, and button styles must be editable.
    
    Theme editor settings:
    Add settings for:
    - Section background color
    - Container max width
    - Desktop layout columns ratio
    - Gap between left and right column
    - Section padding top desktop
    - Section padding bottom desktop
    - Section padding top mobile
    - Section padding bottom mobile
    
    Left content settings:
    - Heading text
    - Heading color
    - Heading font size desktop
    - Heading font size mobile
    - Heading font weight
    - Body text
    - Body text color
    - Body text font size desktop
    - Body text font size mobile
    - Body max width
    - Airline card background color
    - Airline card text color
    - Airline card border radius
    - Airline card font size desktop
    - Airline card font size mobile
    - Airline card padding
    - Airline card gap
    - Airline card 1 text
    - Airline card 2 text
    - Airline card 3 text
    - Airline card 4 text
    - Airline card 5 text
    - Airline card 6 text
    - Button text
    - Button link
    - Button background color
    - Button text color
    - Button border radius
    - Button font size
    - Button height
    - Button max width
    - Trust text under button, rich text or multiline text
    - Trust text color
    - Trust text font size
    
    Right comparison settings:
    - Savings badge text
    - Savings badge background color
    - Savings badge icon text, default €
    - Savings badge icon background color
    - Savings badge icon text color
    - Savings badge text color
    
    Comparison card 1 settings:
    - Card 1 background color
    - Card 1 border color
    - Card 1 price text
    - Card 1 main text
    - Card 1 label text
    - Card 1 text color
    
    Comparison card 2 settings:
    - Card 2 background color
    - Card 2 border color
    - Card 2 price text
    - Card 2 main text
    - Card 2 label text
    - Card 2 text color
    
    Default content:
    Heading:
    Handbagage-ready — sla de check-in rij over
    
    Body text:
    Ontworpen om slimmer te reizen zonder zware koffer. Neem je outfits, schoenen en essentials georganiseerd mee en bespaar op onnodige ruimbagagekosten.
    
    Airline cards:
    KLM
    Transavia
    TUI fly
    Ryanair
    easyJet
    Brussels Airlines
    
    Button text:
    Kies jouw Roolo Reistas
    
    Button link:
    #MainProduct-template--product
    
    Trust text:
    ✓ 82+ beoordelingen   ✓ 30 dagen garantie
    
    Savings badge:
    Gebaseerd op mogelijke ruimbagagekosten
    
    Comparison card 1:
    Price: €0,00
    Main text: Geen ruimbagage nodig
    Label: Roolo
    
    Comparison card 2:
    Price: €65+
    Main text: Extra kosten & wachten
    Label: Andere koffers
    
    Default colors:
    - Section background: #fbf7f4
    - Heading color: #281b1b
    - Body text color: #111111
    - Airline card background: #ffffff
    - Airline card text: #202020
    - Button background: #382928
    - Button text: #ffffff
    - Savings badge background: #eeeae7
    - Savings badge icon background: #382928
    - Savings badge icon text: #ffffff
    - Comparison card 1 background: #382928
    - Comparison card 1 text: #ffffff
    - Comparison card 2 background: #ffffff
    - Comparison card 2 text: #281b1b
    
    Make sure the section is clean on mobile and that empty airline card fields do not leave blank spaces.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-airline-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_bg_color }};
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top_mobile }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.column_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font_weight }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.body_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_font_size_mobile }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.body_max_width }}px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: {{ block.settings.airline_card_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.airline_card_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.airline_card_text_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.airline_card_padding }}px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.airline_card_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.airline_card_font_size_mobile }}px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.button_height }}px;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.button_max_width }}px;
    width: 100%;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-trust-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.trust_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.trust_text_font_size }}px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.savings_badge_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.savings_badge_text_color }};
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.savings_badge_icon_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.savings_badge_icon_text_color }};
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-comparison-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-comp-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    border: 2px solid;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-comp-card-1-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_1_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.card_1_text_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.card_1_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-comp-card-2-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_2_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.card_2_text_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.card_2_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-comp-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-comp-main-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-airline-savings-comp-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-airline-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top_desktop }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-airline-savings-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: {{ block.settings.desktop_columns_ratio }};
    }

    .ai-airline-savings-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-airline-savings-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.body_font_size_desktop }}px;
    }

    .ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.airline_card_font_size_desktop }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<airline-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-airline-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-airline-savings-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-airline-savings-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-airline-savings-left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-airline-savings-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.body_text != blank %}
          <div class="ai-airline-savings-body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.body_text }}</div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-airline-savings-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.airline_card_1 != blank %}
            <div class="ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.airline_card_1 }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.airline_card_2 != blank %}
            <div class="ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.airline_card_2 }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.airline_card_3 != blank %}
            <div class="ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.airline_card_3 }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.airline_card_4 != blank %}
            <div class="ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.airline_card_4 }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.airline_card_5 != blank %}
            <div class="ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.airline_card_5 }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.airline_card_6 != blank %}
            <div class="ai-airline-savings-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.airline_card_6 }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        {% if block.settings.button_text != blank %}
          <a href="{{ block.settings.button_link }}" class="ai-airline-savings-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.button_text }}
          </a>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.trust_text != blank %}
          <div class="ai-airline-savings-trust-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.trust_text }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-airline-savings-right-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.savings_badge_text != blank %}
          <div class="ai-airline-savings-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-airline-savings-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.savings_badge_icon_text }}</div>
            <span>{{ block.settings.savings_badge_text }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-airline-savings-comparison-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-airline-savings-comp-card-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if block.settings.card_1_price != blank %}
              <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.card_1_price }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.card_1_main_text != blank %}
              <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-main-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.card_1_main_text }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.card_1_label != blank %}
              <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.card_1_label }}</div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-airline-savings-comp-card-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if block.settings.card_2_price != blank %}
              <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.card_2_price }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.card_2_main_text != blank %}
              <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-main-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.card_2_main_text }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.card_2_label != blank %}
              <div class="ai-airline-savings-comp-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.card_2_label }}</div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</airline-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class AirlineSavings{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
      }
    }

    customElements.define('airline-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }}', AirlineSavings{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

